<template><div><h2 id="number-system" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#number-system" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Number System</h2>
<p>The number system or the numeral system is the system of naming or representing numbers. We know that a number is a mathematical value that helps to count or measure objects and it helps in performing various mathematical calculations. There are different types of number systems in Maths like decimal number system, binary number system, octal number system, and hexadecimal number system. In this article, we are going to learn what is a number system in Maths? different types, conversion procedures with many number system examples in detail. Also, check <a href="https://byjus.com/maths/what-is-mathematics/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">mathematics for grade 12<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> here.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>编号系统或数字系统是命名或表示数字的系统。我们知道数字是一种数学值，它有助于计数或测量物体，并有助于执行各种数学计算。数学中有不同类型的数字系统，如十进制数系统、二进制数系统、八进制数系统和十六进制数系统。在这篇文章中，我们将学习什么是数学中的数字系统?不同的类型，转换程序与许多数字系统的例子详细。另外，点击这里查看<a href="https://byjus.com/maths/what-is-mathematics/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">12年级数学<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>。</p>
</blockquote>
